\phi(\lambda x+(1-\lambda)y)\leq \lambda \phi(x)+(1-\lambda)\phi(y) - \frac{c(1-\lambda)\lambda}{2}\|x-y\|^2 
c>0
\forall\lambda \in[0,1]
\phi
\psi(x) = \phi(x) - c \|x\|^2
